### <span class="smallcaps">The Duty of Using Reason: and of Taking No Dogma On Trust</span>

<span class="smallcaps">It</span> is the bounden duty of all who are not
intellectually incapable of independent thought, to search out the true
meaning of the doctrines they accept, and the foundations of these
doctrines in Reason.

